main.value: JSON is a light-weight, language independent, data interchange format.		See http://www.JSON.org/		The files in this packageimplement JSON encoders/decoders in Java.		It also includes the capability to convert between JSON and XML, HTTP		headers, Cookies, and CDL.This is a reference implementation. There is a large number of JSON packages		in Java. Perhaps someday the Java community will standardize onone. Until		then, choose carefully.		The license includes this restriction: "The software shall be used for good,		not evil." If your conscience cannot live with that, then choose a different		package.
